summary: An Ordinance granting to J. M. Weistling, Bertha L. Fairbairn, Manville S. Booth, W. C. Leslie and M. R. Raymer, permission and authority to improve the alley in block 7 of Ayer & Walker's Addition to the City of Seattle, and in Block 3 of Hazeltine Heights Addition to the City of Seattle, by grading the same at their own cost and expense.
